  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/4d6569abc440c3cd8d1266277d8fd36c.poster.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/4d6569abc440c3cd8d1266277d8fd36c.webm?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/4d6569abc440c3cd8d1266277d8fd36c.mp4?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/9cb0de018e17f43823e37924257daac2.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/96aa8550559fa0a9669564bae9bcdc76.webp?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five years ago, The Viscount and its crew set sail through The Pale Passage in search of absolute magnetic South. The ship and its crew were tragically lost to the ice, never to be seen again. Her sister ship, The Temperance shall follow in her path, hoping to find answers where The Viscount failed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/a5ce87138f64c2b33f9a595d2cf59093.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A polar exploration game set in an unforgiving frozen wasteland where you embark on a treacherous voyage across the ice and through the Pale Beyond. It’s a stunning yet harsh landscape that can change at any moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5cd1f0af4f75561dcf5bad2d6a9ddb5d.poster.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5cd1f0af4f75561dcf5bad2d6a9ddb5d.webm?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5cd1f0af4f75561dcf5bad2d6a9ddb5d.mp4?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision matters and the ice doesn’t care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the expedition unfolds and the Polar Winter approaches, every decision you make will have a meaningful impact on the story as you navigate your way across the ice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/0675ed04c51ac4f60ef4ddca122406bb.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You didn’t ask to lead this expedition, but here you are. Stuck in the ice, Captain missing, miles from civilisation. Someone has to take charge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your meagre resources, balance safety and morale, make the hard calls, and head in the only direction you can - through The Pale Beyond.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/e799455fceabaf91b516d03bb1a4f98c.poster.avif?t=1767787380\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/e799455fceabaf91b516d03bb1a4f98c.webm?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/e799455fceabaf91b516d03bb1a4f98c.mp4?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keeping the crew (and sled dogs) safe, fed, and warm during the expedition is imperative. Surviving the ice will matter little in the face of a mutiny. Every vote will count. So keep the crew on your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/1ebed440406dd162369fb05b60698173.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring original musical compositions, shanties and accordion tunes that will dynamically evolve alongside your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE DEVELOPER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5190275e8364eaf285b30c8e4f4030ec.avif?t=1767787380\" width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saltstone Studios is located in Belfast, Northern Ireland. Their first game was The Pale Beyond, a story-driven survival management game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The team is interested in exploring novel systems-based narrative games that combine the kind of deep choice and consequence narratives you find in interactive fiction, with extensive systems more common from other genres - all designed to bring in-depth worlds and characters to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each title draws direct influences from the complex history of Ireland and Britain, with extensive literary and historical research. Every pixel, sentence, and musical note, is hand crafted in house with care and attention.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/4d6569abc440c3cd8d1266277d8fd36c.poster.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/4d6569abc440c3cd8d1266277d8fd36c.webm?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/4d6569abc440c3cd8d1266277d8fd36c.mp4?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/9cb0de018e17f43823e37924257daac2.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/96aa8550559fa0a9669564bae9bcdc76.webp?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five years ago, The Viscount and its crew set sail through The Pale Passage in search of absolute magnetic South. The ship and its crew were tragically lost to the ice, never to be seen again. Her sister ship, The Temperance shall follow in her path, hoping to find answers where The Viscount failed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/a5ce87138f64c2b33f9a595d2cf59093.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A polar exploration game set in an unforgiving frozen wasteland where you embark on a treacherous voyage across the ice and through the Pale Beyond. It’s a stunning yet harsh landscape that can change at any moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5cd1f0af4f75561dcf5bad2d6a9ddb5d.poster.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5cd1f0af4f75561dcf5bad2d6a9ddb5d.webm?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5cd1f0af4f75561dcf5bad2d6a9ddb5d.mp4?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision matters and the ice doesn’t care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the expedition unfolds and the Polar Winter approaches, every decision you make will have a meaningful impact on the story as you navigate your way across the ice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/0675ed04c51ac4f60ef4ddca122406bb.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You didn’t ask to lead this expedition, but here you are. Stuck in the ice, Captain missing, miles from civilisation. Someone has to take charge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your meagre resources, balance safety and morale, make the hard calls, and head in the only direction you can - through The Pale Beyond.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/e799455fceabaf91b516d03bb1a4f98c.poster.avif?t=1767787380\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/e799455fceabaf91b516d03bb1a4f98c.webm?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/e799455fceabaf91b516d03bb1a4f98c.mp4?t=1767787380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keeping the crew (and sled dogs) safe, fed, and warm during the expedition is imperative. Surviving the ice will matter little in the face of a mutiny. Every vote will count. So keep the crew on your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/1ebed440406dd162369fb05b60698173.avif?t=1767787380\" width=616 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring original musical compositions, shanties and accordion tunes that will dynamically evolve alongside your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE DEVELOPER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266030/extras/5190275e8364eaf285b30c8e4f4030ec.avif?t=1767787380\" width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saltstone Studios is located in Belfast, Northern Ireland. Their first game was The Pale Beyond, a story-driven survival management game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The team is interested in exploring novel systems-based narrative games that combine the kind of deep choice and consequence narratives you find in interactive fiction, with extensive systems more common from other genres - all designed to bring in-depth worlds and characters to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each title draws direct influences from the complex history of Ireland and Britain, with extensive literary and historical research. Every pixel, sentence, and musical note, is hand crafted in house with care and attention.</p>",
